# Vanessa Furtado Nunes
### Verbo GET – listar todos 
GET http://localhost:8000/funcionario/ HTTP/1.1 

### Verbo GET – listar um 
GET http://localhost:8000/funcionario/4 HTTP/1.1 
### Verbo POST – adicionar 
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/funcionario/ HTTP/1.1 
content-type: application/json

{
    "nome" : "Vanessa", 
    "matricula" : "12345", 
    "cpf" : "0192387455", 
    "telefone" : "49988234567", 
    "grupo" : 1, 
    "senha" : "123456"
} 

### Verbo PUT – atualiza 
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/funcionario/3 HTTP/1.1 
content-Type: application/json

{ 
    "nome" : "Vanessaaaaaaaaaabbbbbb", 
    "matricula" : "12345", 
    "cpf" : "01923874656", 
    "telefone" : "49988234567", 
    "grupo" : 1, 
    "senha" : "testeddddddd" 
} 

### Verbo DELETE - excluir 
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/funcionario/3 HTTP/1.1